Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.15,0:00:55.03,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\blur3\fad(0,0)\i1\move(300,1065,45,1065)}我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.03,0:00:58.16,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(0,150)}哼哼喘着粗气
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.28,0:01:02.24,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(0,150)}沿着走廊一阵风跑来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.16,0:01:06.37,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(0,150)}今晚是你最喜欢吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.46,0:01:09.42,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(0,0)}你想吃的就是这个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.42,0:01:10.50,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\blur3\fad(0,0)\i1}就是这个没错
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.50,0:01:14.59,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(0,0)}加上你就完美了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.59,0:01:19.01,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(0,300)}美食和大家都在等你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.93,0:01:23.02,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(0,0)}我是个围裙男孩
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.22,0:01:27.69,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}围裙男孩 在厨房放连招
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.06,0:01:31.15,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(0,0)}我是个围裙男孩
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.32,0:01:35.74,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,0)}围裙男孩 你的笑容是绝品
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.74,0:01:37.11,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(0,0)}我们家团团圆圆
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.11,0:01:38.41,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(0,0)}笑声满满
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.41,0:01:39.53,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(0,0)}客厅活像乐园
